{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "IT_Security", "channel": "Cybersecurity_Updates", "user": "jason.wong", "message": "Just a heads up, we have noticed an increase in phishing attempts recently. Please be vigilant and report any suspicious emails to the IT department.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "Staff_Training", "channel": "Q2_2025_Training", "user": "JamesKim", "message": "Reminder: Our training session on customer service best practices is scheduled for next week. Please confirm your availability.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "IT_Security", "channel": "Cybersecurity_Updates", "user": "LindaChen", "message": "Thanks for the warning, Jason. I'll remind my team to be on the lookout for suspicious emails.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "Staff_Training", "channel": "Q2_2025_Training", "user": "jason.wong", "message": "James, I've checked my schedule and I'm available for the customer service training next week.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "IT_Security", "channel": "Cybersecurity_Updates", "user": "jason.wong", "message": "Linda, I appreciate your support. Let's ensure our network remains secure.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "Staff_Training", "channel": "Q2_2025_Training", "user": "jason.wong", "message": "Hello team, I'm glad to report on the success of the browser security training we rolled out this quarter. It's been a month since we've conducted the staff training on risky pop-ups and phishing. I've been monitoring the security alerts and I'm happy to say that we've achieved a significant reduction in Chrome security alerts company-wide.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "Staff_Training", "channel": "Q2_2025_Training", "user": "jason.wong", "message": "Based on the data from our IT security system, we've seen a 40% decrease in security alerts since the training. This is a clear indication that the staff has been applying the knowledge they acquired during the training session. Let's continue to strengthen our security measures and keep up the great work, team!", "create_at": 1620500000100}}
